    <item>
      <title>花旗财富负责人西格说不要在野生股票波动中购买蘸酱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/citi-wealth-head-sieg-says-don-t-buy-dip-amid-wild-stock-swings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该银行的全球财富负责人安迪·西格（Andy Sieg）称，花旗集团（Citigroup Inc.）敦促有钱的客户在极端市场波动中保持谨慎，尽管“高峰冲击”可能已经过去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/citi-wealth-head-sieg-says-don-t-buy-dip-amid-wild-stock-swings</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 04:20:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金：中国投资者在贸易战中平静下来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-10/hedge-fund-chinese-investors-calm-amid-trade-war-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[APS资产管理的创始人Wong Kok Hoi表示，中国投资者已适应“敌对”美国对大陆公司的行动。但是，他认为，在“极大的不确定性和非理性”时期，风险溢价已经上升。他与David Ingles和Annabelle Droulers在“彭博：中国秀”上进行了交谈。  （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-10/hedge-fund-chinese-investors-calm-amid-trade-war-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 04:10:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛的Shan说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-10/us-china-trade-likely-to-plummet-goldman-s-shan-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛的Hui Shan告诉彭博电视台，中国政策制定者正在“校准局势”，并权衡他们回应最新的美国关税的选择。虽然对经济的潜力可能高达中国GDP的3％，但Shan表示，通过依靠其他市场，中国仍然可以抵消对美国出口的直接影响是“合理的”。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-10/us-china-trade-likely-to-plummet-goldman-s-shan-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 03:01:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>警惕的亚洲官员试图确保特朗普关税缓刑棒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/wary-asian-officials-seek-to-ensure-trump-tariff-reprieve-sticks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲的官员对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的90天停顿对数十个贸易伙伴的关税持续了90天，并以救济，谨慎和一点嘲笑的混合方式做出了反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/wary-asian-officials-seek-to-ensure-trump-tariff-reprieve-sticks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 02:52:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国库的摇摆触发全球债券市场余震</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/treasuries-chaos-is-triggering-aftershocks-across-global-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国国债市场动荡不安的一天之后，从澳大利亚到日本的债券摇摆不定，随着唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对关税的惊喜停顿，市场迅速降低了降低利率的赌注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/treasuries-chaos-is-triggering-aftershocks-across-global-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 01:43:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者押注刺激</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/chinese-shares-climb-for-third-day-as-investors-bet-on-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股票上涨了第三天，反映了投资者对北京提供更多刺激支持的期望，并希望与美国达成贸易协定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/chinese-shares-climb-for-third-day-as-investors-bet-on-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 01:37:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股票期货在特朗普公布关税缓刑后跳跃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/european-stock-futures-jump-after-trump-unveils-tariff-reprieve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）停止计划对数十个贸易伙伴实施较高的互惠关税的计划之后，欧洲股票期货集会，这减轻了人们对贸易战争扩大的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/european-stock-futures-jump-after-trump-unveils-tariff-reprieve</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 00:49:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Levy混沌之后的黄金攀登18个月以来取得了最大的收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/gold-edges-up-after-levy-chaos-drives-biggest-gain-in-18-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金牌在18个月内发布了其最大的一日收益后再次上升，因为对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税议程的困惑促使投资者购买贵金属作为天堂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/gold-edges-up-after-levy-chaos-drives-biggest-gain-in-18-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 00:30:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票集会延长，债券在波动日之后上涨：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）暂停了他大部分盛大的互惠关税之后，全球金融市场反弹，亚洲股票在两年多以来都发行了他们的增长。在动荡的会议之后，国库会集会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 22:44:15 GMT</pubDate>
